intro.title: Pisinisi Aiga, Musumusuga Pasefika
intro.p1: O le A & S Distributors o se pisinisi aiga e fa'amoemoe i le tautuaina o la matou aiga o tagata fa'atau e fa'alagolago mai ia matou mo mea'ai maualuga mai Fiti, Niu Sila ma Ausetalia. O matou o le Fa'atau o le Itu i Matu o Kalefonia mo The New Zealand Lamb Company ma o lo matou lava fale USDA mo le tipi o mamoe ma 'oti uma. Matou te ave mai le tele o mea'ai fa'apitoa o le Pasefika e susu, fa'amalo ma mago i tau taugofie.
intro.p2: I le A & S Distributors matou te taumafai mo le lelei sili e ala i le fausia o so'otaga tumau ma a matou tagata fa'atau e ala i lo matou fa'amoemoe i le fa'amaoni ma le fa'aaloalo. Matou te tu'uina atu i fale oloa oloa lelei e fa'aaoga e o latou tagata fa'atau e fai ai mea'ai manaia mo o latou aiga.
intro.p3: Matou te taumafai e tu'uina atu se tulaga o auaunaga e le gata e avatu oloa e mana'omia e a matou tagata fa'atau ae fa'apea fo'i le fa'amautu o le sa'o o au fa'atonuga. O le alu i le "maila fa'aopoopo" o le mea lea e ese ai le A & S Distributors mai o matou tagata fa'atau. Matou te fa'atalitali i le galulue fa'atasi ma oe.

australian-goat-diced-prepack.name: 'Oti Ausetalia Tipi Prepack
australian-goat-diced-prepack.description: Aano 'oti Ausetalia tipi ma fa'apusa mo le faia o kare faigofie. Aano mama, manogi e malama i mea'ai kuka tuai. O pusa uma e fa'apusa mo fa'atau oloa faigofie pe kuka aiga.

chicken-sausage-hot.name: Susiti Moa Vevela
chicken-sausage-hot.description: Ituaiga mea manogi o la matou susiti moa ta'uta'ua ma le sili fa'aopoopo ma cayenne pepper. Tu'uina mai le porotini mama lava lea ma le kiki vevela. Lelei mo i latou e fiafia i a latou susiti ma le vevela.

lamb-sausage-2lb.name: Susiti Mamoe
lamb-sausage-2lb.description: Pusa fa'atau oloa faigofie o susiti mamoe faia mai mamoe Niu Sila lelei. O le manogi tu'uese o mamoe e malama i nei laina mea manogi lelei. Lelei mo barbecue aiga ma taeao vaiaso faigaluega.

lamb-sausage-2lb.seoDescription: Susiti mamoe 2lb pusa fa'atau oloa. Mamoe Niu Sila lelei. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.

lamb-sausage-hot.name: Susiti Mamoe Vevela
lamb-sausage-hot.description: Susiti mamoe mea manogi ma le vevela fa'aopoopo mai sili peppers. O le manogi suamalie o mamoe Niu Sila fetaui ma mea manogi malosi mo se susiti e pa. Mo tagata fiafia i le vevela e talia le mamoe lelei.

fish-kawa-kawa-steak-slices.name: I'a Kawa Kawa Steak Slices
fish-kawa-kawa-steak-slices.description: Kawa Kawa tipi i fasi steak faigofie ua saunia mo kuka. O nei tipi mafiafia e lelei mo sulu, pan-searing, pe tunu. O le aano malo e tali lelei le vevela maualuga ma mea manogi malosi.

unicorn-ta.name: Unicorn Ta
unicorn-ta.description: I'a Unicorn (Ta i le gagana Fiti), o se i'a aau tu'uese ma le aano vaivai, suamalie. Ta'ua mo le foliga nifo i lona ulu, o lenei i'a e taua i le Pasefika atoa mo lona manogi mama ma le aano malo.
unicorn-ta.seoTitle: Unicorn I'a Ta Fiti | A & S Distributors
unicorn-ta.seoDescription: I'a Unicorn Fiti (Ta), aano vaivai suamalie. I'a aau tu'uese. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.
unicorn-ta.seoKeywords: i'a Unicorn, i'a Ta, mea'ai sami Fiti, i'a motu Pasefika

kawango.name: Kawango
kawango.description: Kawango, o se i'a aau ta'uta'ua mai Fiti ta'uta'ua mo lona aano malo ma le manogi vaivai. O lenei i'a o se filifiliga fa'aaoga tele e galue lelei ma le tele o auala kuka ma mea manogi. O se mea taua i mea'ai sami motu Pasefika.
kawango.seoTitle: Kawango I'a Aau Fiti | A & S Distributors
kawango.seoDescription: I'a aau Kawango Fiti, malo ma vaivai. Kuka fa'aaoga tele. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.
kawango.seoKeywords: i'a Kawango, i'a Fiti, i'a aau, mea'ai sami Pasefika

roosters-halal.name: Roosters Halal
roosters-halal.description: Roosters halal fa'amaonia (moa taane matua) mo fa'atonuga masani e mana'o ai manu sili manogi, malo. O le taimi tupu umi e fa'atupu ai le manogi moa loloto sili mo supo, stews, ma kare.
roosters-halal.seoTitle: Roosters Halal Fa'amaonia | A & S Distributors
roosters-halal.seoDescription: Roosters halal mo kuka masani. Manogi moa suamalie. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.

white-cassava-2lb.name: Cassava Pa'epa'e
white-cassava-2lb.description: Pusa lapopo'a fa'atau oloa faigofie o cassava a'a pa'epa'e. O lenei starchy e leai se gluten e mafai ona saunia i le tele o auala: fa'avela ma susu niu, falai e fai ai chips, pe fa'amomo. O se fa'avae fa'aaoga tele mo mea'ai masani ma fa'aonaponei.

jackfruit.name: Jackfruit
jackfruit.description: Jackfruit fa'amalo, o le fua laau sili i le lalolagi, taua mo lona aano aano tu'uese. A talavou, o le jackfruit e mafai ona fa'aaogaina o se sui aano i kare ma tacos. O le jackfruit pala e suamalie ma le manogi tropical.
jackfruit.seoDescription: Jackfruit fa'amalo, fua tropical fa'aaoga tele. Filifiliga sui aano. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.
jackfruit.seoKeywords: jackfruit, fua tropical, sui aano, mea'ai motu Pasefika

purple-taro-5lb.name: Talo Viole
purple-taro-5lb.description: Pusa tele o talo viole mo aiga ma tu'uina atu mea'ai. O le aano viole matagofie e faia ai fa'aaliga mata'ina i mea'ai masani ma kuka fusion fa'aonaponei. Manogi eleele, suamalie vaivai e fetaui lelei ma niu.

purple-taro-5lb.seoDescription: Talo viole 5lb pusa aiga. Lanu matagofie, manogi lelei. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.

yellow-taro-2lb.name: Talo Samasama
yellow-taro-2lb.description: Ituaiga talo aano-samasama ma le aano kilimi atu nai lo talo pa'epa'e pe'a kuka. O lenei ituaiga e taua fa'apitoa mo lona aano lamolemole i saunauga fa'amomo ma lona suamalie vaivai. Lelei mo mea'ai lolo (kilimi niu) masani.

yellow-taro-5lb.name: Talo Samasama
yellow-taro-5lb.description: Pusa aiga o talo samasama mo kuka masani. O le aano samasama e fa'aalia ai le tele o beta-carotene. E liu kilimi matagofie pe'a fa'avela ma fetaui matagofie ma susu niu i saunauga motu Pasefika masani.

yellow-taro-5lb.seoDescription: Talo samasama 5lb pusa. Kilimi, mea'ai. Tau fa'atau tele e maua.
yellow-taro-5lb.seoKeywords: talo samasama fa'atau tele, pusa aiga talo, mea'ai motu Pasefika, talo fa'atau tele

paranthas-plain-value-pack.name: Paranthas Plain Value Pack
paranthas-plain-value-pack.description: Paranthas fa'amalo plain (falaoa falag fa'apa') ua saunia e kuka. O nei falaoa flaky, pata e lelei mo taeao ma fuamoa, fa'atasi ma kare, pe fa'atumu ma au mea fiafia. O se mea taua i umukuka Indo-Fiti, ua saunia i minute.

tucker-blitz-bars.name: Tucker Blitz Bars
tucker-blitz-bars.description: Tucker Blitz aisa kimi bars tasi mo mea suamalie tasi faigofie. O le aisa kimi Fiti kilimi lava lea i se ituaiga lima. Lelei mo fa'atau oloa, pati, pe fa'amalieina mana'oga aisa kimi i so'o se taimi.

tuckers-triple-ripple.name: Tuckers Triple Ripple
tuckers-triple-ripple.description: Tuckers Triple Ripple aisa kimi ma manogi manaia e tolu fa'afefiloi fa'atasi. O lenei aisa kimi fa'amalie, lanu o se mea fiafia i tamaiti ma tagata matutua fo'i. Aisa kimi Fiti lelei masani i se ituaiga tele-manogi fa'afiafia.
